      "description": "ch0246_cafe_monolog_1",
      "category": "cafe",
      "text": "真想在这里和大家一起举办一场礼服派对呀～",
      "text_original": "ここでみんなとドレスパーティーしたいな～",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%B5%85%E9%BB%84%20%E7%9D%A6%E6%9C%88/%E7%A4%BC%E6%9C%8D/jp/ch0246_cafe_monolog_1.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0246_cafe_monolog_2",
      "category": "cafe",
      "text": "库呼呼，老师原来喜欢这种感觉的呀？",
      "text_original": "くふふっ、先生ってこういうのが好きなんだ？",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%B5%85%E9%BB%84%20%E7%9D%A6%E6%9C%88/%E7%A4%BC%E6%9C%8D/jp/ch0246_cafe_monolog_2.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0246_cafe_monolog_3",
      "category": "cafe",
      "text": "有没有谁来陪我玩呀～？",
      "text_original": "誰か遊んでくれないかなぁ～？",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%B5%85%E9%BB%84%20%E7%9D%A6%E6%9C%88/%E7%A4%BC%E6%9C%8D/jp/ch0246_cafe_monolog_3.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0246_cafe_monolog_4",
      "category": "cafe",
      "text": "啊咧，欺负一下的话感觉会很有趣呢♪",
      "text_original": "あれ、いじったら面白そう♪",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%B5%85%E9%BB%84%20%E7%9D%A6%E6%9C%88/%E7%A4%BC%E6%9C%8D/jp/ch0246_cafe_monolog_4.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0246_cafe_monolog_5",
      "category": "cafe",
      "text": "库呼呼！真开心呀~感觉，真的很喜欢这个地方呢。",
      "text_original": "くふふっ！楽しいなぁ〜なんか好きなんだよね、ここ",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%B5%85%E9%BB%84%20%E7%9D%A6%E6%9C%88/%E7%A4%BC%E6%9C%8D/jp/ch0246_cafe_monolog_5.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0246_commonskill",
      "category": "battle",
      "text": "稍～微有点烫哦？",
      "text_original": "ちょ～っと熱いよ？",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%B5%85%E9%BB%84%20%E7%9D%A6%E6%9C%88/%E7%A4%BC%E6%9C%8D/jp/ch0246_commonskill.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0246_eventlobby_1",
      "category": "event",
      "text": "恶作剧要像正式演出一样！正式演出要像恶作剧一样♪",
      "text_original": "イタズラは本番のように！本番はイタズラのように♪",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%B5%85%E9%BB%84%20%E7%9D%A6%E6%9C%88/%E7%A4%BC%E6%9C%8D/jp/ch0246_eventlobby_1.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0246_eventlobby_2",
      "category": "event",
      "text": "嗯～……潜入路线的话……应该是那边吧？",
      "text_original": "ん～……潜入ルートはぁ……あっち、かな？",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%B5%85%E9%BB%84%20%E7%9D%A6%E6%9C%88/%E7%A4%BC%E6%9C%8D/jp/ch0246_eventlobby_2.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0246_eventlobby_3",
      "category": "event",
      "text": "怎么？想和睦月酱一起玩吗？库呼呼。",
      "text_original": "なあに？ムツキちゃんと遊びたいの？くふふっ。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%B5%85%E9%BB%84%20%E7%9D%A6%E6%9C%88/%E7%A4%BC%E6%9C%8D/jp/ch0246_eventlobby_3.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0246_eventlobby_4",
      "category": "event",
      "text": "工作结束之后要不要一起去看歌剧？绝对会很有意思哟♪",
      "text_original": "仕事が終わったら一緒にオペラ観に行かない？絶対楽しいよ♪",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%B5%85%E9%BB%84%20%E7%9D%A6%E6%9C%88/%E7%A4%BC%E6%9C%8D/jp/ch0246_eventlobby_4.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0246_eventlogin_1",
      "category": "event",
      "text": "那么那么，这次会有什么样的事件在等着我们呢～？",
      "text_original": "さてさて、どんな事件が待ってるのかな～？",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%B5%85%E9%BB%84%20%E7%9D%A6%E6%9C%88/%E7%A4%BC%E6%9C%8D/jp/ch0246_eventlogin_1.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0246_eventlogin_2",
      "category": "event",
      "text": "这次感觉也会超级有趣！",
      "text_original": "今回もすっごく面白そう！",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%B5%85%E9%BB%84%20%E7%9D%A6%E6%9C%88/%E7%A4%BC%E6%9C%8D/jp/ch0246_eventlogin_2.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0246_exskill_1",
      "category": "battle",
      "text": "库呼呼，上当了吗？",
      "text_original": "くふふ、騙されちゃった？",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%B5%85%E9%BB%84%20%E7%9D%A6%E6%9C%88/%E7%A4%BC%E6%9C%8D/jp/ch0246_exskill_1.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0246_exskill_2",
      "category": "battle",
      "text": "Surprise！",
      "text_original": "サプラーイズ！",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%B5%85%E9%BB%84%20%E7%9D%A6%E6%9C%88/%E7%A4%BC%E6%9C%8D/jp/ch0246_exskill_2.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0246_exskill_3",
      "category": "battle",
      "text": "锵～。猜猜这是什么？",
      "text_original": "じゃーん。これなーんだ？",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%B5%85%E9%BB%84%20%E7%9D%A6%E6%9C%88/%E7%A4%BC%E6%9C%8D/jp/ch0246_exskill_3.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0246_exskill_level_1",
      "category": "battle",
      "text": "快看快看！是可爱的棉花糖哦？",
      "text_original": "ほらほらっ！可愛いわたあめだよ？",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%B5%85%E9%BB%84%20%E7%9D%A6%E6%9C%88/%E7%A4%BC%E6%9C%8D/jp/ch0246_exskill_level_1.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0246_exskill_level_2",
      "category": "battle",
      "text": "啊哈哈！接招吧～",
      "text_original": "あははっ！くらえ～",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%B5%85%E9%BB%84%20%E7%9D%A6%E6%9C%88/%E7%A4%BC%E6%9C%8D/jp/ch0246_exskill_level_2.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0246_exskill_level_3",
      "category": "battle",
      "text": "猜到了吗？",
      "text_original": "予想できたかな？",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%B5%85%E9%BB%84%20%E7%9D%A6%E6%9C%88/%E7%A4%BC%E6%9C%8D/jp/ch0246_exskill_level_3.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0246_exweapon_get",
      "category": "growup",
      "text": "库呼呼♪就是这个～最喜欢这种手感了～",
      "text_original": "くふふっ♪これこれ〜この手応えが好きなんだよね～",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%B5%85%E9%BB%84%20%E7%9D%A6%E6%9C%88/%E7%A4%BC%E6%9C%8D/jp/ch0246_exweapon_get.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0246_formation_in_1",
      "category": "formation",
      "text": "要在这里玩吗？好呀！要玩什么？",
      "text_original": "ここで遊ぶの？いいよ！なにする？",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%B5%85%E9%BB%84%20%E7%9D%A6%E6%9C%88/%E7%A4%BC%E6%9C%8D/jp/ch0246_formation_in_1.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0246_formation_in_2",
      "category": "formation",
      "text": "库呼呼，交给我吧！",
      "text_original": "くふふっ、任せて！",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%B5%85%E9%BB%84%20%E7%9D%A6%E6%9C%88/%E7%A4%BC%E6%9C%8D/jp/ch0246_formation_in_2.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0246_formation_select",
      "category": "formation",
      "text": "什么什么～？要玩什么呀？",
      "text_original": "なになに～？どういう遊び？",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%B5%85%E9%BB%84%20%E7%9D%A6%E6%9C%88/%E7%A4%BC%E6%9C%8D/jp/ch0246_formation_select.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0246_gachaget",
      "category": "growup",
      "text": "库呼呼，睦月酱大变身～！来吧，想让我做什么？尽管说说看？",
      "text_original": "くふふっ、ムツキちゃんだいへんし～ん！さ、何して欲しい？なんでも言ってごらん？",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%B5%85%E9%BB%84%20%E7%9D%A6%E6%9C%88/%E7%A4%BC%E6%9C%8D/jp/ch0246_gachaget.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0246_growup_1",
      "category": "growup",
      "text": "睦月酱好像成长了呢！那么，猜猜～是哪里成长了呢？",
      "text_original": "ムツキちゃん、成長したみたい！さて、どこが成長したでしょ～か？",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%B5%85%E9%BB%84%20%E7%9D%A6%E6%9C%88/%E7%A4%BC%E6%9C%8D/jp/ch0246_growup_1.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0246_growup_2",
      "category": "growup",
      "text": "也就是说……我可以做更～厉害的恶作剧了对吧？库呼呼！",
      "text_original": "これってつまり……も～っとすごいイタズラしてもいいってことだよね？くふふっ！",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%B5%85%E9%BB%84%20%E7%9D%A6%E6%9C%88/%E7%A4%BC%E6%9C%8D/jp/ch0246_growup_2.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0246_growup_3",
      "category": "growup",
      "text": "没问题吗？到时候事情要是变麻烦了，我可不管哦～？",
      "text_original": "大丈夫？手に負えなくなっても知らないよ～？",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%B5%85%E9%BB%84%20%E7%9D%A6%E6%9C%88/%E7%A4%BC%E6%9C%8D/jp/ch0246_growup_3.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0246_growup_4",
      "category": "growup",
      "text": "啊哈哈哈！感觉能玩得更开心了！",
      "text_original": "あはははっ！もっと楽しく遊べそう！",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%B5%85%E9%BB%84%20%E7%9D%A6%E6%9C%88/%E7%A4%BC%E6%9C%8D/jp/ch0246_growup_4.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0246_lobby_1_1",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "怎么样？睦月酱看起来像大人一点了吗？",
      "text_original": "どう？ムツキちゃん、大人っぽい？",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%B5%85%E9%BB%84%20%E7%9D%A6%E6%9C%88/%E7%A4%BC%E6%9C%8D/jp/ch0246_lobby_1_1.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0246_lobby_1_2",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "库呼。老实说出来也没关系哦？毕竟今天的我比平时更“大人”嘛。",
      "text_original": "くふっ。正直に言っていいんだよ？今日の私はいつもより\"大人\"なんだから。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%B5%85%E9%BB%84%20%E7%9D%A6%E6%9C%88/%E7%A4%BC%E6%9C%8D/jp/ch0246_lobby_1_2.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0246_lobby_2_1",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "提问！为什么睦月酱会穿着礼服呢！",
      "text_original": "問題でーす！どうしてムツキちゃんはドレスを着ているのでしょう！",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%B5%85%E9%BB%84%20%E7%9D%A6%E6%9C%88/%E7%A4%BC%E6%9C%8D/jp/ch0246_lobby_2_1.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0246_lobby_2_2",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "要是猜对的话，睦月就送你特别的礼 · 物 · 哦～♪",
      "text_original": "当てられたら特別なプレゼントをあ・げ・る♪",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%B5%85%E9%BB%84%20%E7%9D%A6%E6%9C%88/%E7%A4%BC%E6%9C%8D/jp/ch0246_lobby_2_2.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0246_lobby_2_3",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "要是猜错的话，作为惩罚～……就让你来当我的椅子好了♪",
      "text_original": "間違えたら罰として〜……私の椅子になってもらおっかな♪",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%B5%85%E9%BB%84%20%E7%9D%A6%E6%9C%88/%E7%A4%BC%E6%9C%8D/jp/ch0246_lobby_2_3.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0246_lobby_3_1",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "今天来玩点比平时更大人一点的游戏吧。",
      "text_original": "今日はいつもより大人っぽい遊びをしようよ。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%B5%85%E9%BB%84%20%E7%9D%A6%E6%9C%88/%E7%A4%BC%E6%9C%8D/jp/ch0246_lobby_3_1.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0246_lobby_3_2",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "至于玩什么嘛……老师来决定也可以哦？",
      "text_original": "何をするかは……先生が決めていいよ？",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%B5%85%E9%BB%84%20%E7%9D%A6%E6%9C%88/%E7%A4%BC%E6%9C%8D/jp/ch0246_lobby_3_2.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0246_lobby_4_1",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "刚才有人叫我“大姐姐”呢。是因为穿着礼服的关系吗？",
      "text_original": "さっき「お姉さん」って呼ばれちゃった。ドレス着てたからかな？",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%B5%85%E9%BB%84%20%E7%9D%A6%E6%9C%88/%E7%A4%BC%E6%9C%8D/jp/ch0246_lobby_4_1.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0246_lobby_4_2",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "库呼呼。想让老师也这么叫我一次呢～？",
      "text_original": "くふふっ。先生からも呼ばれてみたいな～？",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%B5%85%E9%BB%84%20%E7%9D%A6%E6%9C%88/%E7%A4%BC%E6%9C%8D/jp/ch0246_lobby_4_2.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0246_lobby_5_1",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "这件礼服，是我和便利屋的大家一起挑的哦。",
      "text_original": "このドレス、便利屋のみんなと選んだの。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%B5%85%E9%BB%84%20%E7%9D%A6%E6%9C%88/%E7%A4%BC%E6%9C%8D/jp/ch0246_lobby_5_1.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0246_lobby_5_2",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "因为是承载着特别回忆的衣服嘛，所以我想珍惜地穿着它。",
      "text_original": "特別な思い出の服だからね、大切に着たいんだ。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%B5%85%E9%BB%84%20%E7%9D%A6%E6%9C%88/%E7%A4%BC%E6%9C%8D/jp/ch0246_lobby_5_2.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0246_login_1",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "欢迎光临，老师！居然让穿着礼服的可爱睦月酱等这么久，老师可真会摆架子呢~",
      "text_original": "いらっしゃい、先生！ドレス姿の可愛いムツキちゃんを待たせるなんて、いいご身分だねぇ？",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%B5%85%E9%BB%84%20%E7%9D%A6%E6%9C%88/%E7%A4%BC%E6%9C%8D/jp/ch0246_login_1.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0246_login_2",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "这边这边！今天要玩什么呀？",
      "text_original": "こっちこっち！今日は何して遊ぶ？",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%B5%85%E9%BB%84%20%E7%9D%A6%E6%9C%88/%E7%A4%BC%E6%9C%8D/jp/ch0246_login_2.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0246_memoriallobby_1",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "我说？别看我这样，其实我可是相当信赖着老师的哦？",
      "text_original": "あのね？こう見えても私、結構信頼してるんだよ？先生のこと。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%B5%85%E9%BB%84%20%E7%9D%A6%E6%9C%88/%E7%A4%BC%E6%9C%8D/jp/ch0246_memoriallobby_1.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0246_memoriallobby_2_1",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "诶，很意外吗？……是因为我总是在恶作剧吗？",
      "text_original": "え、意外？……いつもイタズラばっかりしてるから？",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%B5%85%E9%BB%84%20%E7%9D%A6%E6%9C%88/%E7%A4%BC%E6%9C%8D/jp/ch0246_memoriallobby_2_1.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0246_memoriallobby_2_2",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "库呼呼。我也不是对谁都会这么做的啦。",
      "text_original": "くふふっ。私だって誰彼構わずやるわけじゃないって。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%B5%85%E9%BB%84%20%E7%9D%A6%E6%9C%88/%E7%A4%BC%E6%9C%8D/jp/ch0246_memoriallobby_2_2.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0246_memoriallobby_3_1",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "所以嘛，……那笔钱要怎么处理，就交给老师决定啦。",
      "text_original": "まあ、だから……そのお金をどうするかは、任せるよ。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%B5%85%E9%BB%84%20%E7%9D%A6%E6%9C%88/%E7%A4%BC%E6%9C%8D/jp/ch0246_memoriallobby_3_1.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0246_memoriallobby_3_2",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "老师的话，一定会把它用在有意义的地方的吧？",
      "text_original": "先生なら、ちゃんと意味のあることに使ってくれるでしょ？",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%B5%85%E9%BB%84%20%E7%9D%A6%E6%9C%88/%E7%A4%BC%E6%9C%8D/jp/ch0246_memoriallobby_3_2.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0246_memoriallobby_3_3",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "拿去捐给什么地方也好，当成老师的活动资金也可以……",
      "text_original": "どっかに寄付してもいいし、先生の活動資金にしてもいいし……。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%B5%85%E9%BB%84%20%E7%9D%A6%E6%9C%88/%E7%A4%BC%E6%9C%8D/jp/ch0246_memoriallobby_3_3.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0246_memoriallobby_4_1",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "要是都不想样的话，就当作是老师帮我保管好了——",
      "text_original": "それが嫌なら、先生が預かるってことにして――",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%B5%85%E9%BB%84%20%E7%9D%A6%E6%9C%88/%E7%A4%BC%E6%9C%8D/jp/ch0246_memoriallobby_4_1.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0246_memoriallobby_4_2",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "为了我们的未来先存起来，这样好像也不错呢？",
      "text_original": "私たちの未来のために取っておいても、いいかもね？",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%B5%85%E9%BB%84%20%E7%9D%A6%E6%9C%88/%E7%A4%BC%E6%9C%8D/jp/ch0246_memoriallobby_4_2.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0246_memoriallobby_5",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "诶？你问我在说什么？",
      "text_original": "え？何を言っているのかって？",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%B5%85%E9%BB%84%20%E7%9D%A6%E6%9C%88/%E7%A4%BC%E6%9C%8D/jp/ch0246_memoriallobby_5.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0246_memoriallobby_6",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "库呼呼！谁知道呢？到底会是什么意思呢♪",
      "text_original": "くふふっ！さあ？どういう意味だろうね♪",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%B5%85%E9%BB%84%20%E7%9D%A6%E6%9C%88/%E7%A4%BC%E6%9C%8D/jp/ch0246_memoriallobby_6.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0246_relationship_up_1",
      "category": "growup",
      "text": "老师啊，你真的明白……自己正在做的事情意味着什么吗？库呼呼。",
      "text_original": "先生さぁ、自分がやってることの意味……ちゃんと分かってるの？くふふ。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%B5%85%E9%BB%84%20%E7%9D%A6%E6%9C%88/%E7%A4%BC%E6%9C%8D/jp/ch0246_relationship_up_1.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0246_relationship_up_2",
      "category": "growup",
      "text": "啊哈哈！我也最——喜欢老师了！各种意义上都是哦♪",
      "text_original": "あははっ！私も先生のこと、だーい好き！いろんな意味でね♪",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%B5%85%E9%BB%84%20%E7%9D%A6%E6%9C%88/%E7%A4%BC%E6%9C%8D/jp/ch0246_relationship_up_2.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0246_relationship_up_3",
      "category": "growup",
      "text": "哼～……这种感情叫什么，我可是知道的。如果在意的话，要不要我告诉你呀？",
      "text_original": "ふぅん……この感情の名前、私知ってる。気になるなら、教えてあげよっか？",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%B5%85%E9%BB%84%20%E7%9D%A6%E6%9C%88/%E7%A4%BC%E6%9C%8D/jp/ch0246_relationship_up_3.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0246_relationship_up_4",
      "category": "growup",
      "text": "诶～？嗯～？原来如此。老师是想和我变得更～要好呢。",
      "text_original": "へ～？ふーん？そっかあ。先生は、も～っと私と仲良くなりたいんだね。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%B5%85%E9%BB%84%20%E7%9D%A6%E6%9C%88/%E7%A4%BC%E6%9C%8D/jp/ch0246_relationship_up_4.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0246_season_birthday_1",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "啊哈哈！谢谢老师来给我庆祝♪",
      "text_original": "あははっ！お祝いしてくれてありがと、先生♪",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%B5%85%E9%BB%84%20%E7%9D%A6%E6%9C%88/%E7%A4%BC%E6%9C%8D/jp/ch0246_season_birthday_1.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0246_season_birthday_2",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "想着老师也许会高兴，所以我试着穿上了礼服……怎么样？开心吗？",
      "text_original": "先生が喜ぶかなって思ってドレスを着てみたんだけど……どう？嬉しい？",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%B5%85%E9%BB%84%20%E7%9D%A6%E6%9C%88/%E7%A4%BC%E6%9C%8D/jp/ch0246_season_birthday_2.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0246_season_birthday_player_1",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "老师，今天是你的生日对吧？",
      "text_original": "先生、今日誕生日だよね？",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%B5%85%E9%BB%84%20%E7%9D%A6%E6%9C%88/%E7%A4%BC%E6%9C%8D/jp/ch0246_season_birthday_player_1.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0246_season_birthday_player_2",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "那就来开派对吧！派对♪",
      "text_original": "じゃあパーティーしよっ！パーティー♪",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%B5%85%E9%BB%84%20%E7%9D%A6%E6%9C%88/%E7%A4%BC%E6%9C%8D/jp/ch0246_season_birthday_player_2.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0246_season_halloween_1",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "我的礼服为什么是红色的……猜得到为什么吗？",
      "text_original": "私のドレスが赤い理由……なんでか分かる？",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%B5%85%E9%BB%84%20%E7%9D%A6%E6%9C%88/%E7%A4%BC%E6%9C%8D/jp/ch0246_season_halloween_1.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0246_season_halloween_2",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "因为沾上血的话也不会太显眼——",
      "text_original": "血がついても目立たないから――",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%B5%85%E9%BB%84%20%E7%9D%A6%E6%9C%88/%E7%A4%BC%E6%9C%8D/jp/ch0246_season_halloween_2.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0246_season_halloween_3",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "开玩笑的！啊哈哈！被骗到了吗～？",
      "text_original": "なーんて！あははっ！騙された～？",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%B5%85%E9%BB%84%20%E7%9D%A6%E6%9C%88/%E7%A4%BC%E6%9C%8D/jp/ch0246_season_halloween_3.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0246_season_newyear_1",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "老师，新年快乐～希望今年也会是开心的一年呢♪",
      "text_original": "先生、あけおめ～今年も楽しい一年になるといいね♪",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%B5%85%E9%BB%84%20%E7%9D%A6%E6%9C%88/%E7%A4%BC%E6%9C%8D/jp/ch0246_season_newyear_1.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0246_season_newyear_2",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "老师也是这么想的吧？",
      "text_original": "先生もそう思うでしょ？",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%B5%85%E9%BB%84%20%E7%9D%A6%E6%9C%88/%E7%A4%BC%E6%9C%8D/jp/ch0246_season_newyear_2.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0246_season_xmas_1",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "在圣诞节穿礼服这件事，会不会有什么特别的意义呢？",
      "text_original": "クリスマスにドレスを着るのって、何か特別な意味があるのかな？",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%B5%85%E9%BB%84%20%E7%9D%A6%E6%9C%88/%E7%A4%BC%E6%9C%8D/jp/ch0246_season_xmas_1.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0246_season_xmas_2",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "要不要一起查查看？库呼呼。",
      "text_original": "一緒に調べてみない？くふふっ。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%B5%85%E9%BB%84%20%E7%9D%A6%E6%9C%88/%E7%A4%BC%E6%9C%8D/jp/ch0246_season_xmas_2.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "CH0246_Title",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "蔚蓝档案！库呼呼！",
      "text_original": "ブルーアーカイブ！くふふっ！",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%B5%85%E9%BB%84%20%E7%9D%A6%E6%9C%88/%E7%A4%BC%E6%9C%8D/jp/CH0246_Title.ogg"
    }
  ],
